data.description: One level living at it's best! The beautiful mountain view home has tons of open space and 3 bedrooms on the main level for a very comfortable mountain life style. Some level area but not to much yard if you prefer the natural look. Open kitchen area with plenty of cabinets and space to move around if there are 2 cooks in the kitchen and an actual laundry room with outdoor access. The lofted area has a bedroom with its own bathroom as a bonus. All rooms have walk-in closets and are spacious. For outdoor living you have a nice back yard with concrete retaining wall and on the front you have a "Rocking Chair" Covered Porch. This home is nicely tucked away in a small community 5 minutes from Hiawassee &even closer to Lake Chatuge. Family is present in the home, please allow at least 2 hours notice for viewing.
